  m_text: 'You pilot the spaceship that starts out in the middle of the screen. You
    must destroy each cargo ship, and it''s break away containers, by shooting them
    into smaller pieces until they disappear. Besides firing, your ship can turn,
    thrust, and warp to a random location.


    Upon destroying every cargo container,
    you advance to the next stage. Boss spaceships occasionally appear and fire bullets
    at your ship and at the cargo containers. You must avoid contact with every cargo
    container, boss, or bullet.


    1 hit and you''re dead!'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
