    - target: {fileID: 6045351305608797148, guid: 2226f9b7b0df0854c9c87a916480fc8e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: Good strategy means killing as many of these as possible. The small
        boss enemy can only enter from the sides, like the large one. It, however,
        tracks your Ship when firing. It always shoots slightly in front of you or
        slightly behind you. Treat the small boss ship with the respect it deserves.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
