      propertyPath: m_text
      value: All Cargo Ships appear on the screen initially large. You must break
        them up into smaller pieces. The first screen sends forth four large Cargo
        Ships. Up to 11 are eventually released on later levels. (Note that only
        26 cargo ships/containers are allowed on the screen at one time, so if there
        are already 26 when a large Cargo Ship is destroyed, only one medium Cargo
        Container will appear)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
